<html>

<head>
    <% include ../partials/head %>
    <script src="js/visual.js"></script>
    <script src="js/fix_map_height.js"></script>
    <script async defer src="https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/js?key=AIzaSyAoOnmeOfTKrMCM9fwH15jBJ1jnMaR49YI&libraries=visualization&callback=initMap"></script>
</head>

<body>

    <!-- Introduction Section -->
    <div class="container">
        <div id="banner" class="jumbotron">
            <div class="row text-center white-black-shadow">
                <h1>Neighborly Bus Routes</h1><br>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 cointainer">
                <a href="/visual">View Larger Map</a>
                <div style="width:100%; height:300;" id="map"></div>
            </div>
            <div id="intro" class="col-md-6">
                <h3>We hope to provide a more direct communication between public transportation authorities and their loyal
                passengers. We believe it is important for public organizations to have feedback from the people that they
                serve and that areas that are underserved by public transportation, should certainly have more of a
                voice. </h3>
                <h3>Sign up to submit your commutes to help improve your local transit system.</h3>
            </div>
        </div>


        <div class="row">
            <!-- login -->
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <form class="form-horizontal well" method="post" action="#">

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="login-email" class="cols-sm-2 control-label">Your Email</label>
                        <div class="cols-sm-10">
                            <div class="input-group">
                                <span class="input-group-addon"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-envelope" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" name="email" id="login-email" placeholder="Enter your Email" />
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="login-password" class="cols-sm-2 control-label">Password</label>
                        <div class="cols-sm-10">
                            <div class="input-group">
                                <span class="input-group-addon"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-lock" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
                                <input type="password" class="form-control" name="password" id="login-password" placeholder="Enter your Password" />
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group ">
                        <button type="submit" id="login-btn" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-block login-button">Login</button>
                    </div>

                    <div id="login-error"></div>

                </form>

            </div>

            <!-- SIgnup -->
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <form class="form-horizontal well" method="post" action="#">

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="signup-email" class="cols-sm-2 control-label">Your Email</label>
                        <div class="cols-sm-10">
                            <div class="input-group">
                                <span class="input-group-addon"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-envelope" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" name="email" id="signup-email" placeholder="Enter your Email" />
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="signup-password" class="cols-sm-2 control-label">Password</label>
                        <div class="cols-sm-10">
                            <div class="input-group">
                                <span class="input-group-addon"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-lock" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
                                <input type="password" class="form-control" name="password" id="signup-password" placeholder="Enter your Password" />
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="signup-confirm" class="cols-sm-2 control-label">Confirm Password</label>
                        <div class="cols-sm-10">
                            <div class="input-group">
                                <span class="input-group-addon"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-lock" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
                                <input type="password" class="form-control" name="confirm" id="signup-confirm" placeholder="Confirm your Password" />
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group ">
                        <button type="submit" id="register-btn" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-block login-button">Register</button>
                    </div>

                    <div id="signup-error"></div>

                </form>

            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <% include ../partials/footer %>
    <script>
        startApp();
    </script>
</body>

</html>
